race.comment: CARBONARA (10) just ran into one better at Doomben at the latest outing and Melbourne Cup-winning hoop Dolan sticks. Is benefited by a number of key scratchings and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. UNIQUELY FAMOUS (8) was well in the betting on debut and where there's smoke there's fire. Draws favourably and has to be included in calculations. TASSORATI (14) will be better with race experience in the locker and must be respected out of the Gollan yard. Top-three credentials. TOBY'S TRUSTY (7) presents at the races for the first time and any market support must be noted. ILKLEY ROAD (4) next in line from the inside alley.
